      "rationale": "Large-deformation nonlinear static analysis with frictional contact (μ=0.2, Ti-alloy on Ti-alloy) and bilinear isotropic hardening material model for Ti-6Al-4V. Geometric nonlinearity activated. Simplifying assumptions (homogeneous material, nominal geometry from CAD) documented and assessed as appropriate for the compression-bending regime at the validation conditions. Gradation 3 achieved."
