      "rationale": "Eleven (N=11) non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. All constructs sourced from the same production lot as the commercial device. Dimensional inspection via CMM confirmed conformance to nominal drawing within ±0.05 mm. Gradation 3 requirements met."
    },
    {
