      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single ASTM F1717-mandated offset distance (50 mm) and single loading rate (5 mm/min). While the protocol is standardized, only one test condition was evaluated, limiting the ability to assess model behavior across the loading envelope. Required Gradation 3 not achieved; achieved Gradation 2. This is the one factor below required level, consistent with the COU description."
