      "rationale": "One-to-one correspondence established between each of the 11 FEA model instances and the corresponding physical construct: CMM-measured geometry used as model input, material properties from same lot, boundary conditions replicating test fixture geometry (per ASTM F1717 fixture drawings). Traceability matrix documented. Gradation 3 achieved."
