      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly linked to the clinical performance claims in the 510(k) submission. These QoIs are mechanistically linked to the fatigue and fracture failure modes of concern. Gradation 3 requirements met."
